high_descs: Pick up the sponge from the tub.
Bring the sponge to the sink.
Wet the sponge with water in the sink.
Bring the sponge to the metal rack.
Put the sponge on the rack.
anns.task_desc: Put a wet sponge on the metal rack.

high_descs: Turn around, go straight, then turn left to go to the tub.
Pick up the sponge from in the tub.
Turn around and go to the sink behind you.
Wash the sponge in the sink.
Go to the rack to your left.
Place the sponge on the rack, above the spray bottle.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean sponge on the rack.

high_descs: turn around and walk over to the bathtub on the left
grab the sponge out of the bathtub
turn around and walk to the sink ahead
rinse the sponge out in the sink
move to the left a bit and face the drying rack in the corner of the room
place the sponge on the drying rack
anns.task_desc: place a clean sponge on the drying rack
